{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"offline","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/offline_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当浏览器失去网络连接时，<code>offline</code>事件被触发。并且<code>navigator.onLine</code>的值变为&nbsp;<code>false</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常规信息","title":"常规信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"规范\">规范</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/offline.html#event-offline\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"external\">HTML5 Offline</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"接口\">接口</dt>\n <dd>Event</dd>\n <dt id=\"是否冒泡\">是否冒泡</dt>\n <dd>否</dd>\n <dt id=\"可取消默认行为\">可取消默认行为</dt>\n <dd>否</dd>\n <dt id=\"目标对象\">目标对象</dt>\n <dd>当前网页 (<code>&lt;window&gt;</code>)</dd>\n <dt id=\"默认行为\">默认行为</dt>\n <dd>无</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">属性</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">类型</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>产生该事件的对象 (DOM 树中最顶级的那个对象).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件类型。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>该事件是否冒泡。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>该事件是否可取消默认行为。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-offline","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Window.offline_event"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/online_event\"><code>online</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"常规信息","id":"常规信息"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"相关事件","id":"相关事件"}],"summary":"当浏览器失去网络连接时，offline事件被触发。并且navigator.onLine的值变为 false。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: offline event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Offline","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Window: Evenement offline","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.onoffline","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/offline_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/offline_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/offline_event","title":"offline"}],"pageTitle":"offline - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}